{
  "stem": "26731.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But it was quite difficult, what to do with the various levels of Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I managed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That is correct.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, at that, I still remember distinctly bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time was rationing, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the synagogue, the one that was saved by the fire department, was still there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were scheduled to have the bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Actually, it was so cold at that time, they didn't have it in the main sanctuary.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had a kind of-- I think the-- it was the-- the everyday sanctuary, I think it was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I remember distinctly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And actually, at that time, my mother went around to certain bakeries.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you could persuade them, they were nice to-- we got some cake and sweets above the ration card.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember that distinctly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the Levetzow Street.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The same one I mentioned where-- that--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, thanks to the fire department who just waited for the gangs to leave and rushed in immediately.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've been told you could see it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The first two rows were actually immediately put the fire out about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually, I believe I actually didn't even read from the Torah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just said the brachot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then actually it was all-- before that, they had to have special instruction.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at that time for the Hebrew I read.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't too much time to get the instruction.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Therefore, I-- I even knew my [NON-ENGLISH], the laws.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But actually I had-- before I actually-- to bar mitzvah, I had to pass an examination.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had to appear before the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- but I still remember it was very nice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And each bar mitzvah got a set of prayer books.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not too many.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, I would say, about 50, 60 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no that was fine.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
